\id GAL GALATIANS Matupi Chin Standard Bible 
\h GALATI 
\toc1 GALATI 
\toc2 Galati 
\toc3 Gal 
\mt1 GALATI CAPAT  
\mt4 (Letter to the Galatians)  
\is2 GALATI CAPAT  
\im He kah ca he Asia Minor kah Galati hlang boel rhoek ham a tael pah. Paul amah he caeltueih tang la om tih, a olthang khaw oltak ni tite a cimphan la a thui. (1.1-10).  
\ip Paul he caeltueih tak tak ni. Anih he namtom taengah missionary la Boeipa loh a tueih tih Jerusalem ah tah caeltueih taktak la a pom. (1.18—-2.10). Peter he namtom rhoek kah caak ok kawng dongah kapyik kapyok la a om dongah Paul loh rhaprhap a toel (2.1—18). Tangnah he hi khangnah daemnah longpuei la a om. Abraham kah tangnah kawng a tip la Paul rhep rhep a thui. Galati capat he AD 57vaengah a tael.  
\iot Sawt Yoeinah  
\io1 Caeltueih taktak neh olthang taktak \ior (1. 1-10)\ior*  
\io1 Pathen loh Paul a tuek \ior (1. 11-24)\ior*  
\io1 Paul loh amah olthui te a huul \ior (2. 1-21)\ior*  
\io1 Tangnah rhangneh daemnah \ior (3. 1—4. 31)\ior*  
\io1 Mueihla kah hoihaengnah \ior (5. 1—6. 10)\ior*  
\io1 Rhalrhingnah \ior (6. 11-18)\ior*  
